    <body>
        <div><h2>Body mass Index</h2>
    <label for="altura">Height (cm): </label>
    <input id="altura" type="number" min="100" max="250"><br>
    <label for="peso">Weight (kg): </label>
    <input id="peso" type="number" min="0" max="350"><br>
    <button onclick="calcularIMC()">Calculate BMI</button>
    <div id="resultadoIMC"></div>
    <div id="extra">
      
     <h1>Consider the table below to regulate your weight healthily.</h1>
      <pre>
***************************************************************
|    BMI            |          CATEGORY                       |
|-------------------------------------------------------------|
| Until 18,5        |  Under weight                           |
| From  18,5 - 24,9 |  Healthy                                |
| From  25,0 - 29,9 |  Overweight                             |
| From  30,0 - 39,9 |  Obese                                  |
| Over 40     |  Extreme or high risk of obesity              |
***************************************************************
      </pre>
  <h1>Empiricism - based on own experience.</h1>
  <script>
  <p>Carbohydrates generate more hunger sensation and consequently we end up eating more.</p>
  <p>In the morning give preference for fruits.</p>
  <p>At lunch give preference to meats and salads.</p>
  <p>At dinner also give preference for meats and salads.</p>
  <p>Other nutrients should be inserted into the diet weightily depending on their maintenance or weight loss.</p>
  <p>Carbohydrates should be reduced depending on their maintenance or weight loss. Eat carbohydrates preferably in the morning, prioritizing wholemeal product.</p></div>
